  "3166070": {
    "name": "被动勇者：100天拯救世界！",
    "steam_appid": 3166070,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166070/extras/5a9cae515bad1d1d699651b7afab89e1.avif?t=1764108966\" width=617 height=74 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你被一位自称司掌生命与丰饶的女神选中，召唤到了异世界！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，正当你准备大展拳脚时，她却不慌不忙地丢下一颗惊天炸弹：这个世界将在 100 天后被魔王毁灭。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更糟糕的是，她的魔力在召唤你时被耗尽，所以： </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      1. 她完全不知道魔王是谁、在哪、又有多强； </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     2. 你只能使用被动技能； </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     3. 她经常用“没魔力了”当借口偷懒。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这场拯救世界的旅途，从一开始就绝望又奇怪——但你并非孤军奋战。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这位废柴女神决定陪你一起上路！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >奇怪的是，她身上偶尔会散发出一种……海鲜的味道？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在最后的 100 天里，探索这个濒临毁灭的世界，邂逅性格各异的伙伴，开启一段无法预测的冒险吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166070/extras/02ade596150cd0ca850e5ba02966b31b.avif?t=1764108966\" width=617 height=74 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166070/extras/111a97919fbf78959bc20e5a0bb7d4d9.poster.avif?t=1764108966\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166070/extras/111a97919fbf78959bc20e5a0bb7d4d9.webm?t=1764108966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166070/extras/111a97919fbf78959bc20e5a0bb7d4d9.mp4?t=1764108966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166070/extras/b6c448341fd206fcb573f3a594d377ba.poster.avif?t=1764108966\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166070/extras/b6c448341fd206fcb573f3a594d377ba.webm?t=1764108966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166070/extras/b6c448341fd206fcb573f3a594d377ba.mp4?t=1764108966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(另外还有两个隐藏角色！）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166070/extras/cb27bee3d45ca3c0b630b0586270a3dd.avif?t=1764108966\" width=617 height=74 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>地下城探索</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>实时×回合制融合战斗</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>组合技能触发连锁反应</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>永久强化属性的道具</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>城镇中的日常生活</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>攻略美少女</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>收集“愿望”</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>钓鱼！以及一些别的小游戏</strong></p></li></ul>",
